{"tid":1631820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真聽日仲去睇戲食飯玩既，我真係好睇唔起你地","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:18.000Z","uid":88981,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7923dc7d3072c7ef9d5e43a6d867d8627c892ee0","tid":1631820,"uid":88981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"成日都好多人，人地革命緊遊行緊發夢緊，大家仲有心機去睇戲，去溜冰，去玩<br />\n依啲人係乜撚野心態我想問<br />\n當中好多人仲公然講自己係發夢，好撚威<br />\n聽日再去玩既話我真係 好睇唔起你地<br />\n<br />\n利申做戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6660d63990f1c2b082111c4c7aeb4cdfe124d14","tid":1631820,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>文宣國際線要你幫手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6d5128d1148c1c072ec2b577abbfe376bc81cfc","tid":1631820,"uid":88981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6660d63990f1c2b082111c4c7aeb4cdfe124d14","tid":1631820,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>文宣國際線要你幫手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"一定推"},{"pid":"fcadd3c8a43ceabd3feb2926690a7c001c735391","tid":1631820,"uid":88981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5beb954021cb09c047171b53dbbcb9e35c4fcc6c","tid":1631820,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cedf7141d98135759996b48f028332729ef539d4","tid":1631820,"uid":28435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:54.000Z","msg":"咁你唔罷工？"},{"pid":"e62be9bd2eeeb1596cf3c4976251a4de4e84c808","tid":1631820,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"8c64b28d2687daaa7fa2a4886dd38a8a6181215f","tid":1631820,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"拜山點睇<br />\n聽日重陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578962c50d1fea0ec5c12168eda9540e0f78258b","tid":1631820,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97810cd23e229bb6aadf11e91b497478fa095363","tid":1631820,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"咁你咪一樣返工"},{"pid":"88342cad90da2d0ab4bcb1bfc42b4062b76db275","tid":1631820,"uid":88981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c64b28d2687daaa7fa2a4886dd38a8a6181215f","tid":1631820,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"